Yobe State Governor, His Excellency, Hon. Mai Mala Buni on Sunday appeared before the All Progressives Congress (APC) screening Committee to recontest his office. Governor Buni was accompanied by his political associates from within and outside the state, to the Hilton Transcorp Hotel Abuja, the venue of the screening. The state APC Chairman, Alh. Muhammadu Gadaka and the Chief of Staff to the Governor Alh. Abdullahi Yusuf Gashua both accompanied the Governor to the screening exercise. -Advertisement- Similarly, Federal lawmakers representing the state, Hon. Tijjani Zanna Zakariya, Lawan Shettima, Zakariya’u Galadima, Khadijah Abba Ibrahim, Ibrahim Umar and a former Member Ismaila Gadaka were also on the Governor’s entourage.